    "Externe Logger": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "External Loggers"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Externe Logger können geloggte QSOs (und N1MM zusätzlich Spots) per UDP an HAM-Tools senden. Jeder Eintrag entspricht einem Listener auf einem Port mit einem Protokoll-Adapter. Mehrere Bridges können parallel laufen, solange die Ports unterschiedlich sind.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "External loggers can send logged QSOs (and, in the case of N1MM, spots as well) to HAM-Tools via UDP. Each entry corresponds to a listener on a port with a protocol adapter. Multiple bridges can run in parallel as long as the ports are different."
          }
        }
      }
    },
