            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "Comma-separated list. An OP switcher appears in the contest form; the selected OP initials end up in the OPERATOR field (Cabrillo + ADIF) for each QSO. Leave empty if Single-Op."
          }
        }
      }
    },
