    "Windom (Off-Center Fed Dipole, OCFD): Speisepunkt liegt bei 36% / 64% der Gesamtlänge. Impedanz am Speisepunkt ≈ 200–300 Ω je nach Band. 4:1 Current Balun auf FT240-43 empfohlen. Arbeitet auf Grundfrequenz und mehreren Oberwellen ohne Antennentuner.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "Windom (Off-Center Fed Dipole, OCFD): Feed point is at 36% / 64% of the total length. Impedance at feed point ≈ 200-300 Ω depending on band. 4:1 current balun on FT240-43 recommended. Operates on fundamental frequency and several harmonics without antenna tuner."
          }
        }
      }
    },
