    "λ/4 Groundplane: Strahler vertikal, Radiale horizontal oder geneigt. Bei 0° Neigung: Impedanz ≈ 36 Ω (λ/4 Stub oder Anpassnetzwerk nötig). Bei 45° Neigung: ≈ 52 Ω (direkt 50 Ω Koax). Mindestens 3–4 Radiale empfohlen. Mehr Radiale verbessern den Wirkungsgrad.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "needs_review",
            "value": "λ/4 Ground plane: Spotlight vertical, radial horizontal or inclined. At 0° inclination: Impedance ≈ 36 Ω (λ/4 stub or matching network required). At 45° inclination: ≈ 52 Ω (directly 50 Ω coax). At least 3-4 radials recommended. More radials improve the efficiency."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "λ/4 Vertikal": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
